about.summary: Python bindings for the docker credentials store API

name: docker-pycreds
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.2.1" %}

package:
  name: docker-pycreds
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: docker-pycreds-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/shin-/dockerpy-creds/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 7882efd95f44b5df166b4e34c054b486dc7287932a49cd491edf406763695351

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - six >=1.4.0
  run:
    - python
    - six >=1.4.0

test:
  imports:
    - dockerpycreds

about:
  home: https://github.com/shin-/docker-pycreds/
  license: Apache-2.0
  summary: 'Python bindings for the docker credentials store API'
  license_file: LICENSE
  license_family: Apache

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
